data.description: Amazing East Texas Farmhouse Styled 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home sitting on approximately 1.25 acres (additional 1.25 acres available)! Open concept, vaulted ceilings, exposed beams, Stone WBFP flanked with bookshelves. Designer kitchen with beautiful island and breakfast bar, walk-in pantry, propane range, granite tops, SS appliances. Elegant Master Ensuite, garden tub, separate vanities and shower, spacious walk-in closet. Inviting front porch, screened back patio perfect for additional outdoor space. Meticulously neat and clean.
